cell greet
  in: name
  out: message
  do: Greet {name} warmly in one sentence.
  ok: message mentions {name}
  ok: message is one sentence

cell wrap
  in: greet.message
  out: text, emoji
  do: Pass the message through and pick an emoji for it.
  ok: text is {greet.message} unchanged
  ok: emoji is a single emoji
